        So I've been building. Not prototypes &mdash; actual shipped things: a
        gamified system-design curriculum with a real pedagogy, a
        museum-style web experience about cinema and technology, a pricing
        intelligence dashboard that pulls structure out of scraped SaaS pages
        with an LLM. The goal is to learn, by shipping, what this new
        toolchain can and cannot do &mdash; and to come to whatever I build next
        with real instincts instead of speculation.
      </p>

